<h2 id="图像浏览对话框"><a href="#图像浏览对话框" class="headerlink" title="图像浏览对话框"></a>图像浏览对话框</h2><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import wx</span><br><span class="line">import wx<span class="selector-class">.lib</span><span class="selector-class">.imagebrowser</span> as imagebrowser</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == ”__main__”:</span><br><span class="line">    app = wx<span class="selector-class">.PySimpleApp</span>()</span><br><span class="line">    dialog = imagebrowser<span class="selector-class">.ImageDialog</span>(None)   </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> dialog<span class="selector-class">.ShowModal</span>() == wx<span class="selector-class">.ID_OK</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        print ”You Selected File: ” + dialog<span class="selector-class">.GetFile</span>()  </span><br><span class="line">    dialog<span class="selector-class">.Destroy</span>()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

